{"tid":1322640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請繼續去投訴鄭柏林同報警","createTime":"2019-07-16T04:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T00:10:45.000Z","uid":127447,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"eb2a473a07b77796ac900a9be0d7e624f42cda85","tid":1322640,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"已再去1823投訴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/y69S5aB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fy69S5aB.jpg&h=b6279066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文如下，可以抄考<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/case/enquiry.aspx?type=enquiry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Fbig5%2Fcase%2Fenquiry.aspx%3Ftype%3Denquiry&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=f77bdfbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/case/enquiry.aspx?type=enquiry</a><br />\n<br />\n詳細情況:<br />\n在今年(2019年)7月14日夜晚9至11期間，警察於新城市廣場鎮壓市民時，一名警員扭斷一名市民手腕，造成嚴重傷害，永久傷殘，乃嚴重傷害他人身體罪行，屬刑事案件。該警員為總督察鄭柏林。 本人已向警察投訴科投訴，又已報案，但得不到回應，故在此投訴警務署及總督察鄭柏林。 本人要求貴部門馬上以書面及電郵答覆。"},{"pid":"b0e9d77f7b297e7b787375a1822600c29104d75c","tid":1322640,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92c948d42db30f520ba502ba8bb5f58bbe664165","tid":1322640,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:03:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f475d5d03c64000ea5de81fada151239833707ad","tid":1322640,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9be95556408c3fb51e1d66f1d455229885f0b8e8","tid":1322640,"uid":30503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"唔好放過條撚樣"},{"pid":"cc61ac36135826fd73edb7508563b5f69a4d929c","tid":1322640,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9be95556408c3fb51e1d66f1d455229885f0b8e8","tid":1322640,"uid":30503,"like":2,"dis